<HEADLINE> S. Africa to Display Its Technologies in New York </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, August 22 (Xinhua) -- A number of South African
technologies are to be displayed at the United Nations' aid and
trade '97 exhibition in New York next month, South Africa's arms
procurer Armscor said today.
</P>
<P>
"This will be the first time that South African equipment and
technologies will be exhibited at a show of this nature," Armscor
said in a statement in Pretoria.
</P>
