medal through Elena Vitrichenko at the 19th World University Games
here on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Vitrichenko, who led after two rotations on Friday, continued her
steady performances this morning and totalled 39.732 points to claim
the title of the individual all-around event at the rhythmic
gymnastics tournament.
</P>
<P>
