<HEADLINE> PLO Official Hails National Unity Forum Results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, August 23 (Xinhua) -- A senior Palestinian official said
today that Palestinian National Authority (PNA) President Yasser
Arafat had reasserted his leadership at the recent National Unity
Conference which grouped different political forces.
</P>
