<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 23 (Xinhua) -- The China Construction Bank
(CCB), a state-owned commercial bank, has recorded a rapid
development in its business in international settlements this
year, a bank source said.
</P>
<P>
CCB's business in international settlements so far this year
has reached 22.56 billion US dollars, a rise of 7.28 billion US
dollars from the same period of last year.
</P>
