bank's branches in the coastal areas, such as those in Fujian,
Zhejiang, Guangdong and Beijing, to expand their client bases.
</P>
<P>
An investment of 700 million yuan (84.34 million US dollars)
designed to expand settlement business last year resulted in an
increase of one billion US dollars in international settlements in
CCB's Fujian branch. The provincial branch's settlement business
is expected to reach 2.5 billion US dollars at the end of this
year. 
