<HEADLINE> Bamboo Culture Festival to Be Held in East China Province </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANGZHOU, August 23 (Xinhua) -- The 1997 Chinese Bamboo Culture
Festival is scheduled for September 8-10 in Anji County, one of
the country's major bamboo producers in east China's Zhejiang
Province.
