<HEADLINE> Two Coca-Cola Hope Primary Schools Built In Shanxi </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TAIYUAN, August 23 (Xinhua)-- Ground has been broken for a
"hope project" primary school funded by the Taiyuan Coca-Cola
Company with 200,000 yuan (24,000 US dollars) in an old
revolutionary area in north China's Shanxi Province.
</P>
<P>
The 2,450-square-meter Hope Project Primary School, in Tongyu
Town, Zhuoquan County, will benefit school-age children in more
