<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 23 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
today rose 31 HK dollars today to close at 3,008 HK dollars a
tael, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in
Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 326.03 U.S. dollars a troy
ounce, up 3.27 U.S. dollars at today's exchange rate of one U.S.
dollar to 7.7445 HK dollars. 
</P>
