Thanking Mahathir and his government for warm welcome and
hospitality accorded to him and his delegation, Li Peng said, "The
several meetings between us were held in a very cordial
atmosphere. We have not only reached consensus on international
and regional issues of common concern, but also made new
achievements regarding bilateral ties."
</P>
<P>
