Friday as thousands of fresh troops arrived to reinforce units
loyal to Cambodian Second Prime Minister Hun Sen in their battle
to seize the country's last royalist base.
</P>
<P>
The fighting has caused thousands of Cambodians to escape from
battle zones to the nearest neighboring country, Thailand.
